I could not verify if this has since been patched, as the decorator was [moved into Confluence Core in private SVN|http://svn.atlassian.com/fisheye/browse/public/contrib/confluence/atlassian-tinymce-plugin/trunk/src/main/resources/wysiwygpopup.vmd].

