The editor sets autonomously the width and height parameters. even if they wasn't set by the page author.

Example 1: {code}!pinholes.avi!{code}

After editing the page with the editor the statement above will be changed to 
{code}!pinholes.avi|width=32,height=32!{code}

Example 2: {code}!pinholes.avi|width=600,height=600, id=media!{code}

After editing the page with the editor the statement above will be changed to 
{code}!pinholes.avi|width=32,height=32, id=media!{code}

This behavior is very annoying because every statement has to be changed manually.

